  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Our infertility unit has started a clinic for women with rheumatological diseases. those
      women are prone to infertility problems and it might be due to their illness or cytotoxic
      treatment . In our study we are going to observe the effect of their disease on ovarian
      reserve. we will assess it by using intravaginal sonography and blood test such as hormonal
      profile and anti-mullerian hormone (AMH).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
